description:
Vendetta is the powerhouse of US, solid muscle, solid skills, she is the definition of strength, and sportsmanship.
Spartica is a rabid, never say quit, demon from hell. She came to US late in the season and got into the tournament based on her first match which was a tag team effort. With collegian wrestling skills she has defeated ranked veterans to get to this semi-quarterfinal match, and is undefeated in this tournament. The Final Four is set, the next three updates will be shown live, clear your schedules.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE
